Steps for the Installation of JDK:

step 1.Search and click on JDK Download for Java download JDK 8.
step 2.Accept license agreement and download Java 8 JDK for your version 32 bit or JDK download 64 bit.
step 3.When you click on the Installation link the popup will be open. and click on I reviewed and accept the License Agreement and you will be redirected to the login screen in order to download the file.
step 4.Once the Java JDK 8 download is complete, run the exe for install JDK.Click Next
step 5.Select the path to install Java in Windows.You can leave it Default.Click next 
step 6.Once we install Java in windows,click Close.
